HEADWORD: disentangled
<hw>disentangled</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>freed from an
entanglement; -- of people or agents.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> extricated, freed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>straightened out.</def>⟦br⟧
